entry.name: >Use FOV Mask
entry.definition: Whether FOV mask used during image acquisition. The Defined Terms are: 0 = no mask used 1 = FOV mask used

entry.name: >FOV Mask Y Cutoff Distance
entry.definition: Hexagonal FOV mask Y cutoff angle.

entry.name: >FOV Shape
entry.definition: GEMS NM system detector type. The Defined Terms are: 1 = 400AC 6 = Optima 7 = MAXXUS 8 = Millennium MPS 9 = Millennium MPR 10 = Millennium MG

entry.name: >Transmission Mask Width
entry.definition: Attenuation correction transmission scan mask width.

entry.name: >Copper Attenuator Thickness
entry.definition: Thickness of transmission scan copper attenuator.
